  <summary date="2019-09-04T20:31:03Z" status="Introduced in House">Stopping Grinch Bots Act of 2018

This bill prohibits the circumvention (e.g.,&#160;via bot technology)&#160;of a website's security measure or technological control for enforcing posted purchasing limits or for managing inventory. A person may not sell a product if the person knows that the product was acquired using such circumvention.</summary>
